NOTICE OF COMPLAINT FILED
A complaint was filed in the Harbor Justice center charging
that on or about 02-13-2010 you committed a violation of section (s)
602.5 (a) PC UNAUTHORIZED ENTRY OF DWELLING
594 (a) (b) (2) (A) PC VANDALISM IN AN AMOUNT UNDER $400
To enter a plea of guilty or not guilty of said charges
you are hereby
notified to appear on 03-26-2010 at 8:30 AM, in Court Room AS POSTED
of the Justice Center below:
HARBOR JUSTICE CENTE
Newport Beach Facility-South
4601 Jamboree Rd. Newport Beach, CA 92660
(949) 476-4650
If you fail to appear at said time and place, a warrant may be issued for
your arrest.
TONY RACKAUCKAS, DISTRICT ATTORNEY
Re: 10S003 98
